the bot in action.

the highlighted rectangle is the action space for the bot.
everything outside the rectangle is ignored.

the cells in dark gray are uninteresting.
these are closed cells wit no numbers.
number cells with no closed cells.
and flagged cells.
nothing can be done with them.

the not highlighted cells in the middle are the interesting cells.
here we can open closed cells or place flags.

the red and green highlighted cells will be clicked.
for now only numbers will be clicked.

red cells have the right number of flags.
that means all closed cells can be opened.
red cells will be left clicked.

green cells have the right number of closed cells around.
that means all closed cells can be flagged.
green cells will be right clicked.
